Zuno has put in place security measures to protect against the loss, misuse and alteration of the information collected. Your data is stored with the data cloud services hosted by AWS on their secure servers. A “firewall” (an internet security device) sits between the Poply website and the internet to help prevent any unauthorized User from accessing any data.
